channel.title: Corruption Reloaded - 317 - Fast Xp - Dedicated Server - Pking/Economy Based
channel.description:
Welcome to Corruption Reloaded!
We are a unique server offering a journey back to the old days of runescape, with fast leveling and a steady economy we can guarantee that you will have a great time playing with us!
Server Features
- Working bosses (GWD, KBD, DKS, ELE) - Working Skills - Fast Levelling - Great Pk System - 24/7 Uptime - Lag Free - Dupe Free - Working Minigames (Barrows, Fight Caves, Pest Control, DuelArena)
- Godswords - Perfect Hybridding
